Program: Outlook
Title: The London Eye
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbr6l
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
Viewing London from the newly opened London Eye on the South Bank. Joining Frederick Dove in the capsule are architects David Marks and Julia Barfield, social historian Anne Kurshan, Sam King of the Windrush Foundation and Jonathan Glover. Also, a report on St Paul's Cathedral which is visible from the Eye. Picture: London Eye, Credit: Getty Images Show less